headline: Bet on 5 Top-Ranked Stocks With Rising P/E
summary: Tap five stocks with increasing P/E ratios to try out an out-of-the-box approach. These stocks include Peloton Interactive, Genpact, Samsara Inc., Kodiak Gas Services Inc. and Omnicom Group.
